SOURCE CODE:
package project2;
                       
import java.util.Scanner;
public class Project2 {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int count,i=0;
        String string;
        count=args.length;
        System.out.println("Number of arguments: "+count);
        while(i<count){
            string=args[i];
            i= i+1;
            System.out.println(i+":"+string);
        }
    }
}

OUTPUT:
Number of arguments: 4
1:Hello
2:How
3:Are
4:You
